node.text:
Thank you all for the support on my first @hartfordlimited ‘because racecar’ collection 🖤 There’s a passion we all share when it comes to cars - and it’s beautiful. 

We are almost completely sold out! Hoodies and hats are gone, and we only have a couple shirts in each color way left. Please tag me in your photos when you receive your gear! We start shipping out tomorrow and I can’t wait to see!

I was happy to work through my birthday knowing I was going to be around some pretty amazing people. What I didn’t expect was @chevrolet to surprise me with a cake and corvette colored balloons (that also match the beautiful ‘68 Camaros behind me) during production 🥲 

Can’t wait to share with you all what we have in the works! And thank you all for the birthday wishes ❤️🖤

node.text: These past couple weeks have been the craziest of my life. From shooting a movie, to landing and having 2 days to put the entire corvette back together for this campaign, to flying to VIR to test the new @cadillac CT5V Blackwing, flying home for 24 hours to run the C8 at Famoso drag strip yesterday, and now headed back to the airport to fly to Detroit for an exciting opportunity with @chevrolet … I am incredibly grateful. Grateful for every single one of you for believing in me. I’m often told my work ethic is crazy, but i believe my dreams are crazier.

node.text:
Have some BIG news to share with you all this tomorrow, which also happens to be my birthday (edit: announcement will be made August 2nd) !! It wasn’t planned to be announced then, but I’m flying home for 24 hours to share the news with you and I’m so excited. 

Thankful to surround myself with some pretty amazing people like my good friend @jonescrow 🙌🏼 thank you for being a part of this project… Can’t wait to share with you all!!

And yes I’m jealous of Jones being able to park cars in his living room 😅

Changed my flights and flew back early from San Fransisco to show support to @stevenaghakhani06 and the premiere for his racing documentary “Pursuit of Speed” directed by @jeffjhart 

Back to regularly scheduled content this week! Thanks for your patience. Expecting something TOP SECRET for the C8 to arrive any day now so make sure you stay tuned!! 😉
